âŒ Common OOP Mistakes

* Overusing inheritance
* Not using `this` correctly
* Forgetting `new` keyword
* Writing large classes

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

âœ… Best Practices

* Use meaningful class names
* Keep classes small
* Prefer composition over inheritance
* Use encapsulation
* Follow DRY principle

